  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a Huge or smaller creature you can see ends its turn within 30 feet of you, you can use your reaction to magically force the creature to make a <strong>Strength saving throw</strong> against your spell save DC, pulling the creature up to <strong>30 feet</strong> toward you to an unoccupied space. If you pull the target to a space within 5 feet of you, you can make a melee weapon attack against it as part of this reaction.</p>\n<p>You can use this reaction a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: This is part of the </em>@Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.K8USLHLdNjgm7cIe]{Perfected Armor}<em> feature.</em></p>\n</section>",
